LD_PRELOAD="" XKB_DEFAULT_LAYOUT=de gamescope -r 240 -w 2560 -h 1440 --force-grab-cursor -- env VKD3D_DISABLE_EXTENSIONS=VK_KHR_present_wait MANGOHUD=1 %command%

preferrably use xrandr to set primary monitor, if the issue is cursor not being grabbed / locked edit the monitor configuration to isolate the primary display so that the mouse won't escape the game.